lyrics:
[Verse]
Happy Birthday, Nirmala, dearest friend,
With wishes warm, our love we send,
In every picture, your spirit transcends,
Sharing photos of your adventures, never end.

[Chorus]
From all your loving Modsec friends,
A chorus of joy we all send,
With good fortune and magical moments, blend,
For you, our beautiful, caring and loving friend.
style: music on Japanese instruments, soundtrack, descent into a dark demonic mine, fear, horror, mine
